EasyXLS.Charts

Class ExcelDataTable

  • System.Object
    • EasyXLS.Drawings.DrawingObject
      • EasyXLS.Drawings.LineDrawingObject
        • EasyXLS.Drawings.FillDrawingObject
          • EasyXLS.Drawings.EffectDrawingObject
            • EasyXLS.Drawings.FontDrawingObject
              • EasyXLS.Charts.ExcelDataTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEffectDrawingObject, IFontDrawingObject

    public class ExcelDataTable
extends FontDrawingObject
    This class stores the data table information like line settings, fill settings, font settings, shadow settings, legend key visibility, horizontal lines visibility, vertical lines visibility, outlines visibility, visibility.
